    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRiccardo\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Dan Bevacqua\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cMy parents loved each other, but their love confused them. Witnessing their marriage was like watching a dog bark at the door when no one\u2019s there.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFiction\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/fiction/7893/riccardo-dan-bevacqua"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDonate to The Paris Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy The Paris Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Paris Review promotes the most exciting writers of the day and supports inquisitive readers the world over.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDonate\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "https://www.theparisreview.org/donate-to-the-paris-review"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBeautiful Losers: On Leonard Cohen\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Nell Zink\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJuly 5, 2022\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cLife could be so lyrical, if it weren\u2019t a novel.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Daily\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOn Leonard Cohen\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/2022/07/05/beautiful-losers-on-leonard-cohen/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMoon\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Esther Yi\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cIt made me sick to imagine just how moist his palms must be.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFiction\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/fiction/7884/moon-esther-yi"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Art of Fiction No. 254\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Sigrid Nunez\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cThis is a hard thing to say, but it\u2019s absolutely true\u2014when I think of the men I\u2019ve been with, every one of them stood between me and my writing.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInterviews\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/interviews/7906/the-art-of-fiction-no-254-sigrid-nunez"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmma Cline, Dan Bevacqua, and Robert Gl\u00fcck Recommend\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy The Paris Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJuly 1, 2022\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPorn star Rocco Siffredi; Tsai Ming-Liang\u2019s Goodbye, Dragon Inn; and Ra\u00fal Zurita\u2019s INRI.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Daily\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Review\u2019s Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/2022/07/01/cline-bevacqua-gluck-recommend/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBob Ross Paints Your Portrait\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Terrance Hayes\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cYou folks at home are welcome to use a thumb.\nUse a pinkie or a pinkie toe. I just want you to enjoy \nyourselves.\u201d \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPoetry\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/poetry/7883/bob-ross-paints-your-portrait-terrance-hayes"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPosters\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Marc Hundley\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThis portfolio is a diary of several weeks Hundley spent earlier this year with the archives of the Review.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tArt & Photography\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/art-photography/7908/posters-marc-hundley"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPleasant Glen\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Emma Cline\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cWas this a test, Lord?\nMaybe.\nTo be decided.\u201d\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFiction\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
